  METHOD get_vendor_and_inv_party_name.
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
* METHOD ID:          ZCL_MFP_DOCUMENT_PO~get_vendor_and_inv_party_name
* DESCRIPTION:        This method is used by the MyFi Purchasing (MFP) UI5
*                     application (Self Service Purchasing (SSP) Release 2).
*                     This method is used for MyFi Documents
*
* AUTHOR:             Stephen Ning (290977SCN), James Southwell (070667JPS)
* CREATE DATE:        30.05.2020
* R/3 RELEASE VERSION: ECC6
*
* ACTIVITY:           AD-11-32-07 - Self Service Purchasing App
* CR Number:          6000001863 - MyFi Purchasing Release 2
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* VERSION CONTROL
*
* Date     Author    CTS Req    Dev Script     Description
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* 30.05.20 290977SCN RD2K919078 DS-11-32-07-01 Created
*          070667JPS
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
    DATA: lv_lifnr TYPE lifnr,
          lv_lifre TYPE lifre.

    IF me->zif_myfi_document~old_ekko IS NOT INITIAL.
      lv_lifnr = me->zif_myfi_document~old_ekko-lifnr.
      lv_lifre = me->zif_myfi_document~old_ekko-lifre.
    ELSE.
      lv_lifnr = me->gs_poheader-vendor.
      lv_lifre = me->gs_poheader-diff_inv.
    ENDIF.

    SELECT SINGLE name1 FROM  lfa1
      WHERE  lifnr  = @lv_lifnr
      INTO @gv_vendor_name.

    SELECT SINGLE name1 FROM  lfa1
      WHERE  lifnr  = @lv_lifre
      INTO @gv_invparty_name.

  ENDMETHOD.


  METHOD in_admin_details.
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
* METHOD ID:          ZCL_MFP_DOCUMENT_PO~in_admin_details
* DESCRIPTION:        This method is used by the MyFi Purchasing (MFP) UI5
*                     application (Self Service Purchasing (SSP) Release 2).
*                     This method is used for MyFi Documents
*
* AUTHOR:             Stephen Ning (290977SCN), James Southwell (070667JPS)
* CREATE DATE:        30.05.2020
* R/3 RELEASE VERSION: ECC6
*
* ACTIVITY:           AD-11-32-07 - Self Service Purchasing App
* CR Number:          6000001863 - MyFi Purchasing Release 2
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* VERSION CONTROL
*
* Date     Author    CTS Req    Dev Script     Description
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* 30.05.20 290977SCN RD2K919078 DS-11-32-07-01 Created
*          070667JPS
* 20/05/21 210983DY  RD2K921041 DS-11-32-07-01 S6000002393: June DFSS release for MyFi Purchasing
*                    Additional code to restrict user to chose payment justification text from dropdown
* 10/10/23 210983DY RD2K924373 DS-11-32-07-01 6000003027: MyFi Continuous Improvement November Rel
*           Additional logic to save Justification Desription for Payment Term selected
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
*    MOVE-CORRESPONDING  gs_contract_deep-admindetails TO me->zif_myfi_document~new_adm_dtl.
    me->zif_myfi_document~new_adm_dtl-sonid = gs_po_deep-sonid.
    me->zif_myfi_document~new_adm_dtl-pay_term_just_dd = gs_po_deep-paymenttermsjustification+0(2).
    me->zif_myfi_document~new_adm_dtl-pay_term_just = zcl_mfp_document=>get_payment_justification_text( iv_payment_just_code = gs_po_deep-paymenttermsjustification+0(2) ).
    me->zif_myfi_document~new_adm_dtl-justificationdescription = gs_po_deep-justificationdescription.
  ENDMETHOD.


