  METHOD zif_myfi_document~fill_deep_entity.
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
* METHOD ID:          ZCL_MFP_DOCUMENT_PO~zif_myfi_document~fill_deep_entity
* DESCRIPTION:        This method is used by the MyFi Purchasing (MFP) UI5
*                     application (Self Service Purchasing (SSP) Release 2).
*                     This method is used for MyFi Documents
*
* AUTHOR:             Stephen Ning (290977SCN), James Southwell (070667JPS)
* CREATE DATE:        30.05.2020
* R/3 RELEASE VERSION: ECC6
*
* ACTIVITY:           AD-11-32-07 - Self Service Purchasing App
* CR Number:          6000001863 - MyFi Purchasing Release 2
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* VERSION CONTROL
*
* Date     Author    CTS Req    Dev Script     Description
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* 30.05.20 290977SCN RD2K919078 DS-11-32-07-01 Created
*          070667JPS
* 04.12.20 220977FKC RD2K920504 DS-11-32-07-01 6000002172: MyFi Purchasing (Release 2.3)
*                                              Incorporate legacy (non-MyFi docs)
* 03/03/21 210983DY  RD2K920554 DS-11-32-07-01 S 6000002250: MyFi Purchasing (Release 2.4 )
*                               Additional code to handle Multi delivery address
* 20/05/21 210983DY  RD2K921041 DS-11-32-07-01 S6000002393: June DFSS release for MyFi Purchasing
*                    Additional code to restrict user to chose payment justification text from dropdown
* 05/11/21 210983DY  RD2K922034 DS-11-32-07-01 S6000002550: MyFi Applications (December Release)
*                    Additional code to enable Multi Account Assignment
* 18.08.22 210983DY RD2K923033 DS-11-32-07-01 S 6000002805: MyFi Continuous Improvement September Release
*                   Condition to fill data based on $expand option
* 03.03.2023 210983DY  RD2K923630 6000002898 MyFi Continuous Improvement April Release
*                    Additional code for display and toggle of delivery addresses
* 10/10/23 210983DY RD2K924373 DS-11-32-07-01 6000003027: MyFi Continuous Improvement November Rel
*           Additional logic to display Justification Desription for Payment Term selected
* 14.03.2024 210983DY RD2K924772    6000003112: MyFi Continuous Improvement Release 2024
*                 Amended logic for new Prepayment and FMS field changes
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------

    DATA:
      ls_headertext TYPE bapimepotextheader.

* Deep entity is not required when UI call is made for specific $expand options
    CHECK  gv_consumption_only IS INITIAL.

    IF me->gv_draft_indicator EQ abap_true.
      /ui2/cl_json=>deserialize( EXPORTING json = me->gs_deep_entity pretty_name = /ui2/cl_json=>pretty_mode-camel_case CHANGING data = me->gs_po_deep ).
    ELSE.
      IF NOT ( me->zif_myfi_document~gv_useraction EQ zif_mfp_constants=>gc_action-odata-edit AND
         me->zif_myfi_document~old_doc_header-status EQ zif_mfp_constants=>gc_doc_status-approved ).
        IF me->zif_myfi_document~old_doc_header-selected_delegate IS NOT INITIAL.
          me->gs_po_deep-approvaldetails-delegateid = zcl_mfp_utilities=>get_pernr_from_user( me->zif_myfi_document~old_doc_header-selected_delegate ).
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.

      me->gs_po_deep-approvaldetails-isaaicompliance  = me->zif_myfi_document~old_doc_header-isaaicompliance.
      me->gs_po_deep-approvaldetails-isfpmapproved  = me->zif_myfi_document~old_doc_header-isfpmapproved.
      me->gs_po_deep-approvaldetails-isasfinapproved  = me->zif_myfi_document~old_doc_header-isasfinapproved.
      me->gs_po_deep-approvaldetails-issection23  = me->zif_myfi_document~old_doc_header-section23.
      me->gs_po_deep-approvaldetails-parentnumber = me->zif_myfi_document~source_doc_num.

*--- son id for legacy get from PO
      IF me->gv_is_legacy = abap_true.
        READ TABLE me->gt_poheadertext INTO ls_headertext
          WITH KEY
            po_number = me->zif_myfi_document~source_doc_num
            po_item = ls_headertext-po_item
            text_id = zif_mfp_constants=>gc_header_text-po-sonid.
        IF sy-subrc = 0.
          me->gs_po_deep-sonid = ls_headertext-text_line.
        ENDIF.

      ELSE.
        me->gs_po_deep-sonid                        = me->zif_myfi_document~old_adm_dtl-sonid.
      ENDIF.

*      me->gs_po_deep-issameaddressforall = abap_true."me->zif_myfi_document~old_doc_header-issameaddressforall.
*      me->gs_po_deep-issameaddressforall = me->zif_myfi_document~old_doc_header-issameaddressforall.
      me->gs_po_deep-paymenttermsjustification    = me->zif_myfi_document~old_adm_dtl-pay_term_just.
      me->gs_po_deep-paymenttermsjustification    = me->zif_myfi_document~old_adm_dtl-pay_term_just_dd.
      me->gs_po_deep-justificationdescription    = me->zif_myfi_document~old_adm_dtl-justificationdescription.
      IF NOT gs_po_deep-contactdetails-invoicecontactemail IS INITIAL.
        DATA(lv_invoicecontact) = gs_po_deep-contactdetails-invoicecontactemail.
      ENDIF.
      MOVE-CORRESPONDING me->zif_myfi_document~old_doc_header TO me->gs_po_deep-contactdetails.
*      gs_po_deep-issameaddressforall = abap_true.
*  updating invoice contact email on Contact details tab will have that captured into change log
      me->gs_po_deep-contactdetails-invoicecontactemail = lv_invoicecontact.
      MOVE-CORRESPONDING me->zif_myfi_document~change_log TO me->gs_po_deep-changelog.
      MOVE-CORRESPONDING me->zif_myfi_document~approval_history TO me->gs_po_deep-approvalhistory.
      CALL METHOD me->get_account_assignment
        EXPORTING
          iv_document    = me->zif_myfi_document~source_doc_num
          it_lineitems   = me->gs_po_deep-purchaseorderlis
        IMPORTING
          et_assignments = me->gs_po_deep-accountassignments.
    ENDIF.
  ENDMETHOD.


  METHOD zif_myfi_document~get_mm_details.
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
* METHOD ID:          ZCL_MFP_DOCUMENT_PO~zif_myfi_document~get_mm_details
* DESCRIPTION:        This method is used by the MyFi Purchasing (MFP) UI5
*                     application (Self Service Purchasing (SSP) Release 2).
*                     This method is used for MyFi Documents
*
* AUTHOR:             Stephen Ning (290977SCN), James Southwell (070667JPS)
* CREATE DATE:        30.05.2020
* R/3 RELEASE VERSION: ECC6
*
* ACTIVITY:           AD-11-32-07 - Self Service Purchasing App
* CR Number:          6000001863 - MyFi Purchasing Release 2
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* VERSION CONTROL
*
* Date     Author    CTS Req    Dev Script     Description
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* 30.05.20 290977SCN RD2K919078 DS-11-32-07-01 Created
*          070667JPS
* 18.08.22 210983DY RD2K923033 DS-11-32-07-01 S 6000002805: MyFi Continuous Improvement September Release
